第三讲：毕竟不同——戏剧和电影的区别

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appnpyAYc6L1468/a_5a9bfbb1711a8_jzNoaOA5

<section style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">有一个特别有意思的现象，知乎上<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“电影”</strong></span>话题下的提问有16万个,关注者有185万人。而<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“戏剧”</strong></span>话题下的提问却不到3000个，关注人数95万人，<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">只有电影关注人数的一半</strong></span>。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">不可否认至今依然有为数不少的<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">戏剧爱好者</strong></span>，可现在戏剧对普罗大众的影响远远不及广泛传播的电影，这也是不争的事实。从大城市到小县城，有很多人看过很多次电影，却没看过一次戏剧。<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">戏剧于普通人而言，既熟悉又陌生。</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">熟悉在于，即使从来没看过戏剧的人，恐怕也知道<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">《恋爱的犀牛》</strong></span>中的经典对白“你是我温暖的手套，冰冷的啤酒， 带着阳光味道的衬衫，日复一日的梦想。”，也曾被<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">《牡丹亭》</strong></span>里“情不知所起，一往而深，生者可以死，死可以生。”所打动。哪怕你没听过前两句，肯定也知道莎士比亚的<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">《哈姆雷特》</strong></span>里那句：“To be, or not to be: that is the question.”。</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnqqfVVFL3445/image/ueditor/99154200_1509798317.gif" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">然而戏剧对很多人依然是陌生的。比起电影，我们接触戏剧的机会要少得多，甚至对它产生许多误解。</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">有人认为戏剧高深莫测，是不可靠近的阳春白雪，避而远之。也有人进了剧院坐在观众席里看得一头雾水，不懂得如何去欣赏反而埋怨票价是电影票的好几倍。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">即使是常看戏剧的人依然会有苦恼：<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">该如何在参差不齐的市场里挑一部好戏，避免自己花钱遭罪看烂戏呢？</strong></span>就更别提真正了解戏剧历史，称得上戏剧行家的人少之又少了。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); width: 100%; padding: 5px 10px; display: inline-block; text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">有了电影，</strong></p><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">为什么人们还需要看戏剧？</strong></p></section><img style="margin-top: -1em; float: left; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnqqfVVFL3445/image/ueditor/15288300_1509798325.png"/> <section style="clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">这在很多人看来是一个不可理喻甚至有点蠢的问题，但却是我们必须弄明白的问题。电影是人类历史上最伟大的发明之一，自然有其独特的魅力所在。可是作为最古老的艺术形式之一的戏剧，也不能被我们忘记，因为其生动的现场总是充满了震撼人心的力量，让我们站在生活之上俯瞰生活。如巴西剧作家奥古斯都·波瓦所说：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我们的艺术最主要的作用之一就是让人们留意日常生活中的种种表演，在这个无所谓哪里是舞台哪里是观众席的地方，演员也同样是观众。<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">我们全都是艺术家：</strong></span>通过戏剧创作，我们学会如何来观察那些本来显而易见，但由于不习惯观察而经常视而不见的东西。我们最习惯的东西变得无法看到：进行戏剧创作能够使日常生活的舞台变得更加亮丽。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnqqfVVFL3445/image/ueditor/90820500_1509798325.gif" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">戏剧的传承和创新需要新鲜血液，需要越来越多的年轻人加入进来，90后新锐戏剧女导演<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">祖纪妍</strong></span>就是其中之一。作为女学霸，她成绩优异多次荣获校级和国家级奖学金。作为女导演，她曾是北大剧星风采大赛十年历史上<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">唯一一位蝉联两届的冠军导演</strong></span>，也是迄今为止唯一一位获得<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">国家艺术基金项目</strong></span>的学生导演，其执导的话剧《早安，妈妈》在全国进行了40余场的巡演，编剧导演的《伊斯坦布尔之夜》<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">戏文杯剧本大赛一等奖</strong></span>，获邀参与国际女性戏剧节展演。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnqqfVVFL3445/image/ueditor/46945900_1509798326.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; font-size: 11px; color: rgb(125, 117, 117); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▲</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">《早安妈妈》海报</span></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">祖纪妍导演风格独特，追求文本的深度和中文的韵律感，擅长色彩与光影的使用和在舞台上实现立体化的视觉观感，试图实现“电影对戏剧”的反哺。其导演的<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">全球首部机器人舞台剧</strong></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">《小王子》</strong></span>采用机器人参与演出，配合无人机、多媒体技术等视觉特效，广受好评。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnqqfVVFL3445/image/ueditor/78148700_1509798326.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">今年以来，祖纪妍继续推出多部力作，莎士比亚第二时期的作品《终成眷属》也被她搬上舞台，凭借独特的风格和不可复制的创意，一经推出就好评如潮。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnqqfVVFL3445/image/ueditor/26276500_1509798327.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnqqfVVFL3445/image/ueditor/55304700_1509798327.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">祖纪妍发现，越来越多的人开始关注戏剧，想要走近戏剧，却不知从何下手。身为戏剧创造者的她也想做连接观众和戏剧的桥梁，把戏剧这个含羞带俏的大姑娘拉到你面前，替你揭开她的面纱。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">于是她来到<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">小锄头课堂</strong></span>，为你带来<span style="color: rgb(22, 54, 85); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">十堂戏剧入门课程</strong></span>。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnqqfVVFL3445/image/ueditor/7755900_1509798328.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">十讲<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 93, 118); box-sizing: border-box;">精品课程</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">十篇<span style="color: rgb(68, 93, 118); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">精炼文章</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">戏剧问题的<span style="color: rgb(68, 93, 118); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">专业</strong></span>答疑</p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">仅需<span style="color: rgb(68, 93, 118); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">69元</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">就能将<span style="color: rgb(68, 93, 118); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">最具潜力</strong></span>的90后女导演请到你身边</p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">成为你的<span style="color: rgb(68, 93, 118); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">戏剧导师</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 93, 118); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnqqfVVFL3445/image/ueditor/97916100_1512273837.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="戏剧大纲.jpg"/></strong></span></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(68, 93, 118); padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 93, 118); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合人群</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp; 想要提高自己的<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">艺术修养</strong>，丰富生活的人</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp; 对戏剧感兴趣却<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">不知如何入门</strong>的人</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp; 对戏剧略知一二想要在<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">专业人士</strong>指导下加深了解的人</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp; 好奇戏剧<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">背后的故事</strong>的人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(68, 93, 118); padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 93, 118); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">订阅须知</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">《祖爷侃戏》</strong>为“音频+图文”专栏。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.本专栏为付费课程，原价99元，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">限时特价69元</strong>，订阅成功后即可永久收听。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.本专栏为虚拟内容服务，已经订阅成功概不退款，请你理解。</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p sty